# The frontend no longer holds an API key. The Groq key lives server-side
# in the Netlify Function at /netlify/functions/chat.js.
#
# To configure for deployment:
#   Netlify dashboard → Site settings → Environment variables
#   GROQ_API_KEY = <your Groq key>
#
# For local development, run from the repo root:
#   netlify dev
# (this starts both Vite and the functions runtime so /.netlify/functions/chat works)
